"description">一些家居达人通过集线盒，轻松理顺这些杂乱物品的摆放，关上门后非常整齐，还不影响使用和维修。</p><h2 id="cl_4">5、螺旋式衣架晒床单</h2><p itemprop="description">南方城市很多人家会入手烘干机，洗床单被罩很简单，而往北方，烘干机就没有那么普遍了。</p><p itemprop="description">所以晾床单被罩，大多都是用自家的晾衣架，一个床单用两个晾衣架撑起来晾晒，麻烦不说还影响美观。</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x75g4/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img alt="见识下中国的家居智慧，这些设计虽小，但也太实用了吧！" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/06/5f2bd493937391126.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">国内家居设计师根据这一痛点，设计出螺旋的床单架，专门可以晾晒床单被罩。螺旋式更立体通风，晾晒效果好，用完可以拆卸收纳，不占地方，对于小阳台和租房的朋友来说，真的是福音。</p><dir><span class="embed-card main-site " style=""><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'螺旋晾床单架','id':'ax0x75g4' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'淘宝精选', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'taobao.com','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://go.smzdm.com/e855be7159825bc7/ca_bb_yc_1515_71001393_10111_0_55_0"  rel="nofollow" ><img ol  alt="见识下中国的家居智慧，这些设计虽小，但也太实用了吧！" class="res_smzdm" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/card/taobao.png"/></a></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'螺旋晾床单架','id':'ax0x75g4' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'淘宝精选', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'taobao.com','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://go.smzdm.com/e855be7159825bc7/ca_bb_yc_1515_71001393_10111_0_55_0"  rel="nofollow" ><span 