设计，也能给卫生间带来整齐划一的视觉感。</p><dir><span class="embed-card main-site " style=""><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'一杆通清洁工具','id':'ax0x75g4' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'淘宝精选', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'taobao.com','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://go.smzdm.com/9ff89e1655219b20/ca_bb_yc_1515_71001393_10111_0_55_0"  rel="nofollow" ><img ol  alt="见识下中国的家居智慧，这些设计虽小，但也太实用了吧！" class="res_smzdm" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/card/taobao.png"/></a></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'一杆通清洁工具','id':'ax0x75g4' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'淘宝精选', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'taobao.com','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://go.smzdm.com/9ff89e1655219b20/ca_bb_yc_1515_71001393_10111_0_55_0"  rel="nofollow" ><span class="card-name res_smzdm">一杆通清洁工具</span></a><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'一杆通清洁工具','id':'ax0x75g4' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'淘宝精选', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'taobao.com','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://go.smzdm.com/9ff89e1655219b20/ca_bb_yc_1515_71001393_10111_0_55_0"  rel="nofollow" ><span class="mall-data res_smzdm">s.taobao.com</span></a><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'一杆通清洁工具','id':'ax0x75g4' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'淘宝精选', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'taobao.com','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://go.smzdm.com/9ff89e1655219b20/ca_bb_yc_1515_71001393_10111_0_55_0"  rel="nofollow" ><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去看看</span></a></span></span></span></dir><h2 id="cl_6"> 7、冰箱上装开瓶器</h2><p itemprop="description">开瓶器其实还是挺常见的，不过设计有趣又好玩的就很少了。国内越来越多的家居设计师把实用和趣味结合，比如把开瓶器设计成如下造型，壁挂在冰箱上。<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x75g4/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img alt="见识下中国的家居智慧，这些设计虽小，但也太实用了吧！" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/06/5f2bd494170691253.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">从冰箱里拿饮料顺手开瓶盖，轻松方便，瓶盖还正好能掉入篮筐，超级完美~</p><h2 id="cl_7">8、伸缩隔板更正衣柜内部布局</h2><p itemprop="description">不少人家的衣柜布局不合理，比如隔板间距过大，导致空间浪费，若是作为挂衣区，高度又不够，非常麻烦。</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x75g4/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img alt="见识下中国的家居智慧，这些设计虽小，但也太实用了吧！" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/06/5f2bd494115b87422.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">通过伸缩隔板能调整这一布局，根据需求增加伸缩隔板数量，让叠放衣物更方便轻松。</p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x75g4/pic_10/' target='_blank'><img alt="见识下中国的家居智慧，这些设计虽小，但也太实用了吧！" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/06/5f2bd4941d5fb908.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><br/></p><p itemprop="description">伸缩隔板应用非常广泛，除衣柜外，还可以用在水槽柜做分隔，用在鞋柜收纳鞋子，橱柜内收纳锅具等等。</p><dir><span class="embed-card main-site " style=""><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'伸缩隔板','id':'ax0x75g4' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'淘宝精选', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'taobao.com','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://go.smzdm.com/1e2d1856cf59f1ae/ca_bb_yc_1515_71001393_10111_0_55_0"  rel="nofollow" ><img ol  alt="见识下中国的家居智慧，这些设计虽小，但也太实用了吧！" class="res_smzdm" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/card/taobao.png"/></a></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'伸缩隔板','id':'ax0x75g4' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'淘宝精选', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'taobao.com','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://go.smzdm.com/1e2d1856cf59f1ae/ca_bb_yc_1515_71001393_10111_0_55_0"  rel="nofollow" ><span class="card-name res_smzdm">伸缩隔板</span></a><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm"></span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'伸缩隔板','id':'ax0x75g4' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'淘宝精选', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'taobao.com','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" h