</span></div><p itemprop="description">②在配方表中白砂糖越靠后越好（越靠后表示含量越低）</p><p itemprop="description">3⃣️可以关注巧克力上有没有以下标签（表示在巧克力业界获得的奖项）</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/akmg99x9/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/06/5f2b77f1e9c658503.png_e680.jpg" title="" alt="Academy of Chocolate Awards英国巧克力协会"/></a>Academy of Chocolate Awards英国巧克力协会</span></p><p itemprop="description" class="image-show-desc">Academy of Chocolate Awards英国巧克力协会</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/akmg99x9/pic_10/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/06/5f2b7855c30787902.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="Great Taste Awards 世界最重大且信誉度最高的食品和饮品奖项"/></a>Great Taste Awards 世界最重大且信誉度最高的食品和饮品奖项</span></p><p itemprop="description" class="image-show-desc">Great Taste Awards 世界最重大且信誉度最高的食品和饮品奖项</p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/akmg99x9/pic_11/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/06/5f2b78a66f8214890.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="International Chocolate Awards国际巧克力大奖"/></a>International Chocolate Awards国际巧克力大奖</span></p><p itemprop="description" class="image-show-desc">International Chocolate Awards国际巧克力大奖</p><h3>例如：</h3>
