.smzdm.com/p/apz0lpo2/pic_11/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/06/5f2c256c2ab4b3591.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="安装完成"/></a>安装完成</span></p><p itemprop="description">半小时装好<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/apz0lpo2/pic_12/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/06/5f2c2583a204c513.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="开机"/></a>开机</span></p><p itemprop="description">    收拾了下<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/canzhuo/" target="_blank">桌子</a>，拍了个完工照片。<br/></p><p itemprop="description">    桌子是宜家299买的，超级实惠，推荐一下。<br/></p><h2 id="cl_3">评测</h2><h3>色域<br/></h3><p itemprop="description">    首先上神奇网站照片，logo清晰。    </p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/apz0lpo2/pic_13/' target='_blank'><img alt="下一代金刚：S2721DGF，戴尔Dell游戏显示器——首发开箱" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/06/5f2c2583cf1fb3609.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">    能看到左右两张图不一样的，证明现实效果比较不错。（左边的会有logo）<br/></p><p itemprop="description">    需要的话自己去测试一下看看——<a href="https://webkit.org/blog-files/color-gamut/comparison.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" rel="nofollow" >webkit.org</a><br/></p><h3>漏光</h3><p itemprop="description">    感觉比LG850控制的要好一些。<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><span class="img_desc"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/apz0lpo2/pic_14/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/06/5f2c2584003f91307.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="漏光测"/></a>漏光测</span></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/apz0lpo2/pic_15/' target='_blank'><img alt="下一代金刚：S2721DGF，戴尔Dell游戏显示器——首发开箱" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/07/5f2c362eef18b5015.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/apz0lpo2/pic_16/' target='_blank'><img alt="下一代金刚：S2721DGF，戴尔Dell游戏显示器——首发开箱" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202008/07/5f2c362fada124480.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href